{"tid":586594,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"<Inception>有冇試過發夢時知自己發緊夢？","createTime":"2018-03-09T16:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T03:55:25.000Z","uid":65024,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"64d61c581192c6c8d1eacdcd6cb0fd2f63eea0d6","tid":586594,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:01:04.000Z","msg":"我試過一次，半夜五點醒左，再訓返，一入夢就知道自己係發緊夢，意志上可以控制好多動作，係夢入面做好多危險野，因為知道自己發緊夢唔係真<br />\n<br />\n最後見玩左咁多野都冇事就試下跳樓，未落到地就醒左"},{"pid":"4f183b60e624f3e0683d5570c3197562c11c9802","tid":586594,"uid":172357,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"成日都會，我有次仲「清醒」到有意識自己係發緊夢 所以想控制個夢 做啲自己想做既野... 仲試過醒極都醒唔到 明明醒左見到自己落左床 但原來仲係張床上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a611c5b2e8e12d094d3edcc98cb74f951812a2e1","tid":586594,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"清醒夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日有"},{"pid":"31f81d8f2969156e255a9d47bafcdcc361338b6f","tid":586594,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多人有？！"},{"pid":"20d1342970767978540a27dbef4ef969d6ece97a","tid":586594,"uid":141681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"五十次以上"},{"pid":"8a8625915bdadc1e3789dc466a57cec0d54a0758","tid":586594,"uid":62482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:11:00.000Z","msg":"不時feel 倒半睡半醒間靈魂就嚟同身體分離"},{"pid":"3c16c7f140f34df1ce124e385b44b98883c722de","tid":586594,"uid":137639,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"試過夢到個女仔主動搵我<br />\n不過我好快就知道自己發緊夢<br />\n因為個女仔根本就無可能主動黎搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0040ff36b4a4b8ce34afde0661731241111457ad","tid":586594,"uid":159136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過夢到個女仔主動搵我<br />\n不過我好快就知道自己發緊夢<br />\n因為個女仔根本就無可能主動黎搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27644ac3aa6c3102eb6132631234dba3963cf0e4","tid":586594,"uid":37746,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:23:55.000Z","msg":"有試過 係入面控制場景同飛 好正 另外可以試出體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d0ea4677607f9f7c7e05f7157127bb1ee543a7","tid":586594,"uid":624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"之前睇過有人教 習慣平時都望個天花板同埋問自己呢個係咪夢<br />\n等一入夢就會向上望 而夢入面個天花板係會奇怪d 令你意識到呢個係夢"},{"pid":"69d0338bc6b8fcf5d5d6af9302704d1b6971e9fc","tid":586594,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"經常性"},{"pid":"23ef2fe9f45a5aaac6920d2192119775d63bba6f","tid":586594,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有試過 係入面控制場景同飛 好正 另外可以試出體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中間有個俾鬼壓嘅現象，次次都卡個度，淨係拉得起上半身，下半身好實抽離唔到身體，迫住醒"},{"pid":"9564f475cf88000c46f5dfb765deb1cc3581976d","tid":586594,"uid":37822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"我一feel到發緊夢 試圖控制就醒 <br />\n但我想發落去"},{"pid":"67bb1a1280e06b00b1a04b118fa20bb92697733b","tid":586594,"uid":9814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:52:07.000Z","msg":"有一排試過可以控制到自己飛上飛落 <br />\n一路跌一路有離心力 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但依家搵唔返果種感覺 應該係果排精神差先係咁發夢"},{"pid":"a8f36b1fce03238db5c4a921ad266648793c025d","tid":586594,"uid":15136,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:55:17.000Z","msg":"反而試過一次係夢醒左但個世界仲好唔真實<br />\n之後再醒多次先知係夢中夢"},{"pid":"feedd7e11a83d93d7ed16d505f0c3fb2d1e15cb0","tid":586594,"uid":167674,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:28:41.000Z","msg":"知道自己發緊惡夢會係咁撐大對眼<br />\n然後就會醒 <br />\n跟住強迫自己過一陣先好再訓<br />\n太快合返埋眼好大機會發返同一個夢"},{"pid":"a516df5128398d935bdb216ad225165f9bd2edc2","tid":586594,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:29:26.000Z","msg":"我女朋友"},{"pid":"8ca5bff1faede56ef7694aecc07e53e7fd734846","tid":586594,"uid":3613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:37:57.000Z","msg":"早幾日個夢入面係咁跑都唔見有人 知道係發緊夢 係夢入面諗左個辦法幫自己醒 一野向前仆低 feel到個離心力就成功醒左 醒左果下好有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e53a0a81cfeba2adc7a7acc7a2e6974339cd48","tid":586594,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"最常見係跳樓迫自己醒"},{"pid":"6cd5d6c113394896f424ff90eb8dd15517407779","tid":586594,"uid":36460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:53:24.000Z","msg":"4 5年前開始完全知 仲可以控制到係個夢到做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果醒一醒 又未醒哂 可以發返岩岩個夢"},{"pid":"abea3b8f188c8ccd1742cb3552abdb18a599b2d6","tid":586594,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"訓前食DHA就做到"},{"pid":"6088c6155e73a11e746b31d563360e6d6e87b8c6","tid":586594,"uid":154264,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:56:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76b57e999f9d681a5825a54ffa7cd39c98164297","tid":586594,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T19:05:48.000Z","msg":"試過發夢 夢見自己發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2edc5d8dadea89c83825ef79b282162559846c","tid":586594,"uid":154697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T19:22:58.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n細細個都成日發夢，好想離開個夢既時候，我唔知點解會極力控制自己去求其一個位跳樓，之後就醒咗，但係我都係有印象自己未跳到落地下(或者望唔到地下)就醒。<br />\n<br />\n試過幾次鬼壓床，做唔到呢個方法，因為自己控制唔到自己，所以以前發惡夢唔驚，因為知道自己可以走到。但係鬼壓床就會好驚。<br />\n<br />\n依家大個咗好少會發到夢，反而好想搵番以前發夢既感覺，大個既夢係自己訓之前諗過既野，訓咗之後會發一d相關既野，你一唔尊心個夢就好快完，所以每次發到夢都會好想爭取一分一秒去做晒想做既野。<br />\n<br />\n係夢入面嗰種感覺好&hellip;滿足，好想再發一次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff83f04bc1647a7d7de030ae9d3b65e4d8c1be0","tid":586594,"uid":168593,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"試過發夢同條女卜緊 醒左之後發唔返 好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61329d0dfe97685fb0b7790606c5a5440b5c1411","tid":586594,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T19:59:22.000Z","msg":"有，發現之後會嘗試控制夢境裏面發展嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8999fae61c2c76ba8fed06986fbc5ba612b3549d","tid":586594,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T20:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有試過 係入面控制場景同飛 好正 另外可以試出體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中間有個俾鬼壓嘅現象，次次都卡個度，淨係拉得起上半身，下半身好實抽離唔到身體，迫住醒</blockquote><br />\n聽過人講話唔好亂咁試 會返唔到去"},{"pid":"07d880348f7c93b18a643bb4306ecc41ff7f6b44","tid":586594,"uid":159539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8999fae61c2c76ba8fed06986fbc5ba612b3549d","tid":586594,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTi